The beginnings of an Emacs major mode for shen.

For more information on shen see
  http://www.lambdassociates.org/specification/shen_1.7.htm

To use put something like the following in your .emacs
  (require 'shen-mode)
  (add-hook 'shen-mode-hook 'paredit-mode) ; <- entirely optional
  (add-to-list 'auto-mode-alist '("\\.shen\\'" . shen-mode))
  (require 'inf-shen) ; <- for interaction with an external shen process
